shareChallenge? challengeId
    rules:
        - ChallengeStatus = Unverified | Ongoing | Finished
        - User can access any challenge by ShowChallenge!
    when.
        User CreateChallenge!
             Can click on button to share its challenge
    when
        Visitor|User access a challenge
            ShowChallenge!   
                user goes to challenge resume 
        then. 
            Can click on button to share the challenge

            

